stories.title: South Africa clinch series with nine-wicket win in Paarl
stories.summary: South Africa have beaten Pakistan by nine wickets and in so doing have clinched the Standard Bank one-day international series, going into the last game in Cape Town, on Wednesday, with an unassailable three-one lead.
